      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can u help me expand on that? like, how can i frame the argument against meritocracy? i want to show why the idea that \"anyone can make it if they work hard enough\" is actually a flawed concept when you look at the racial wealth gap. make it sound really impactful.",
